data.description: Come see this newly remodeled waterfront home. This charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home features new roof 2022, full plumbing re-pipe as well as whole home electrical rewire with new panel. Enjoy cooking in your new updated kitchen with new cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Home also has recessed lighting and updated bathrooms. Features a detached 2 car garage and a beautiful walk out deck perfect for your outdoor grill. Property backs to canal.  Conveniently located to major interstate 95, 295, River City Shopping and Downtown
